description: Futurex Crypto Projects is a community of futuristic applications based on a secure blockchain and powered by a strong, digital payment system backed by Futurex Crypto. Futurex Crypto is an innovative digital payment currency that can be used for making payments for things, including cryptocurrencies (trading), anywhere in the world. Futurex platform will enable third-party service providers to develop and launch their apps on the Futurex’s secure blockchain and use Futurex Crypto for in-app payments.
name: FUTUREXCRYPTO
